<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="deeply-adv">deeply <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'diːpli/    美 /'diːpli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(程度) 深深地；强烈地；非常地；认真地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>sleep / breathe deeply</strong>
沉睡/深呼吸</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>think deeply about sth</strong> 
认真考虑某事</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My mindless words must have hurt him deeply.  
我那些无心的话一定深深地伤害了他。</p><footer>2013 湖北</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>breathe deeply</strong> 
深呼吸</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I have been <strong><em>_</em></strong>(深深地) impressed by a number of experiences in her life.   （2010 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. deeply  </p></div>